OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly blocks Chinese       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcontrol of tyre giant      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FPirelli                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy has moved to block a Chinese     
OL,6, state-owned company from taking control
OL,7, of tyre making giant Pirelli.          
OL,9,FThe decision is part of measures       
OL,10,Fannounced by Italy's government to     
OL,11,Fprotect Pirelli's independence.        
OL,13,FBeijing-controlled chemical giant      
OL,14,FSinochem is Pirelli's biggest          
OL,15,Fshareholder, with a 37% stake in the   
OL,16,F151-year-old Milan-based firm.         
OL,18,FIt comes as tensions between Beijing   
OL,19,Fand the West are in focus as the US    
OL,20,Fsecretary of state visits China.       
